<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Page Not Found</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f3f4f6;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
            margin: 0;
            text-align: center;
            color: #333;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        h1 {
            font-size: 80px;
            margin: 0;
            color: #ff6b6b;
        }
        h2 {
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-top: 10px;
            color: #444;
        }
        p {
            color: #666;
            margin: 20px 0;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        .home-button {
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            background-color: #007bff;
            color: white;
            border-radius: 4px;
            font-size: 16px;
            transition: background-color 0.3s;
        }
        .home-button:hover {
            background-color: #0056b3;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>404</h1>
        <h2>Oops! Page Not Found</h2>
        <p>It seems the page you're looking for doesn't exist or has been moved.</p>
        <a href="/" class="home-button">Go to Home</a>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
